1
00:01:30,870 --> 00:01:35,100
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:38,229
[2006]

3
00:01:38,150 --> 00:01:38,880
Xia Xiaolan,

4
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,310
you're not allowed to
go out with him anymore!

5
00:01:40,310 --> 00:01:42,039
You're not worthy of him at all!

6
00:01:42,150 --> 00:01:42,759
Who?

7
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,039
Don't play dumb here!

8
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,200
I saw everything during the New Year!

9
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,710
You'd better know your place!

10
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:48,560
Or next time,

11
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,200
it won't just be a verbal warning!

12
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:50,600
Got it.

13
00:01:51,430 --> 00:01:52,070
Move!

14
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:57,640
There are always obstacles
on the road to happiness.

15
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,570
As long as you keep moving forward,

16
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,200
no one can stop you

17
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,400
from finding it.

18
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:06,040
[Episode 28: Happiness No One Can Stop]

19
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:11,400
Sir!

20
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,260
Coming!

21
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:14,590
One bowl of sampan porridge

22
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:16,120
and a plate of braised meat.

23
00:02:16,230 --> 00:02:16,760
Alright.

24
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,680
And a dozen oysters

25
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,930
and a bottle of beer.

26
00:02:22,190 --> 00:02:23,680
A dozen oysters, one beer.

27
00:02:24,030 --> 00:02:24,960
Forget the beer.

28
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,170
Two herbal teas.

29
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,810
And one order of stir-fried rice noodles.

30
00:02:27,810 --> 00:02:29,410
Alright, please have a seat.

31
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,470
Zhou Cheng?

32
00:02:35,910 --> 00:02:36,430
San,

33
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,900
don't drink if you're driving later.

34
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,079
You're here to help me

35
00:02:40,079 --> 00:02:41,810
deal with that bastard, right?

36
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:43,360
Hello.

37
00:02:44,210 --> 00:02:45,540
Why didn't Ge Jian come?

38
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:48,710
I'm here to ask you to go back with me.

39
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,360
Let me ask you—

40
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:52,590
if it had been Xiaolan

41
00:02:52,590 --> 00:02:53,920
who got beaten up today,

42
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,430
could you just let it go?

43
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:57,160
Could you take that lying down?

44
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:59,000
Of course, I wouldn't let it go.

45
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,400
But I also wouldn't be so reckless as to

46
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:02,310
charge over there and pick a fight.

47
00:03:02,310 --> 00:03:02,710
San,

48
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:04,560
fighting isn't going to

49
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,240
solve anything right now.

50
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,300
Alright, alright.

51
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:08,630
I never liked hearing you talk like that.

52
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:10,120
No matter how we solve it later,

53
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,240
today I have to

54
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,640
settle this score first!

55
00:03:12,910 --> 00:03:13,570
Zhou Cheng.

56
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,329
It's fine if you don't want to help,

57
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:17,690
but don't get in my way.

58
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,840
The mahjong parlor is crowded at night.

59
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,240
Do you want to wait until dawn

60
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,190
to make your move?

61
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:29,240
Or follow him home

62
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:30,680
and beat him up

63
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,200
somewhere secluded?

64
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,470
You know

65
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:36,640
that this is Ke Yixiong's turf.

66
00:03:36,870 --> 00:03:38,190
They have the numbers.

67
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,440
You can't act rashly.

68
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,280
Of course.

69
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,400
I, Pan Baohua,

70
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:45,280
am no reckless fool.

71
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,280
Ke Yixiong has been
on the streets for so long.

72
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,010
You think he's a reckless fool?

73
00:03:50,710 --> 00:03:52,570
Wouldn't he
have already thought of all this?

74
00:03:52,570 --> 00:03:54,680
He showed up in broad daylight,
bold as anything.

75
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,079
What if it's a trap?

76
00:03:57,910 --> 00:03:58,710
You rush over,

77
00:03:58,910 --> 00:03:59,630
beat him up,

78
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,680
injure him,

79
00:04:01,030 --> 00:04:01,840
or worse, cripple him...

80
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,370
Alright!

81
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:05,370
I know what you're getting at.

82
00:04:05,630 --> 00:04:06,710
I've already

83
00:04:07,030 --> 00:04:07,870
thought all that through

84
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:09,000
on my way here.

85
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:10,960
At worst,

86
00:04:11,470 --> 00:04:13,470
I'll just be locked up for a few days.

87
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:14,590
When I get out,

88
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:17,000
I'll still be a man to be reckoned with!

89
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:20,970
Enjoy your food.

90
00:04:23,470 --> 00:04:24,800
You get to play the hero.

91
00:04:25,630 --> 00:04:26,960
But what about Zhenzhu?

92
00:04:28,430 --> 00:04:29,430
You're gambling

93
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:32,310
your entire future just to help her.

94
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:33,240
This will always

95
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,390
stand between you.

96
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:38,440
Then I guess you might as well
never see each other again.

97
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:52,950
I...

98
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:56,840
I didn't think that far.

99
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,420
I just wanted to help Sis Zhenzhu.

100
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:01,770
I wanted to avenge her!

101
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,330
Then think about it now.

102
00:05:04,310 --> 00:05:05,240
Just think about

103
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:06,510
how Zhenzhu is.

104
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:09,560
And think about your future together.

105
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:18,430
Do you still remember

106
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:20,290
what your attackers looked like?

107
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,390
I definitely can't

108
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:22,560
remember all of them.

109
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,120
But

110
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,480
there was one

111
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,060
with dyed yellow hair,

112
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:27,160
a sharp face,

113
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:27,820
and a tattoo

114
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,630
on his arm.

115
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:30,360
His name is Qiang.

116
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,690
He was there yesterday.

117
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,840
You remember him so clearly.

118
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,600
I used to run a small stall

119
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:38,440
at Renmin Bridge.

120
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,750
He came around often.

121
00:05:41,070 --> 00:05:42,159
You know how it is—

122
00:05:42,159 --> 00:05:43,430
we stay alert

123
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,070
to those types when doing business,

124
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,720
so we don't get taken advantage of.

125
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,320
You were right to stay alert.

126
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:49,680
What about the others?

127
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,740
Do you remember anything about them?

128
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,409
It's okay. No rush. Take your time.

129
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:59,720
I think there was one
with a scar on his face.

130
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:02,390
I've seen him before

131
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:04,680
at the long-distance bus station.

132
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,270
Officer,

133
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,030
even though it was raining yesterday,

134
00:06:08,030 --> 00:06:09,040
they made quite a commotion

135
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,510
when they attacked.

136
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,000
You could ask around the neighborhood.

137
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,460
There might be witnesses.

138
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:14,980
We'll look into it.

139
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,730
Watch your step.

140
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:25,160
Xiaolan.

141
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:28,120
Sis Zhenzhu.

142
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,250
I was reckless.

143
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:30,920
I almost made things worse.

144
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:33,120
I don't deserve to be your brother.

145
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,430
San,

146
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:37,440
you were just trying to stand up for me.

147
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,240
This isn't on you.

148
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,820
I didn't think it through.

149
00:06:46,430 --> 00:06:47,070
Well...

150
00:06:47,270 --> 00:06:49,000
Let's talk over food, shall we?

151
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,360
I drove all night.

152
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,159
I'm starving.

153
00:06:51,390 --> 00:06:51,790
Right.

154
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:53,090
Let's eat first.

155
00:06:59,430 --> 00:07:00,830
Let me see.

156
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,270
This one, one of these.

157
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:03,720
Wei!

158
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,040
Sis Bai.

159
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:05,630
Here, here.

160
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:06,270
Sit down.

161
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,360
And...

162
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,560
t-these two as well.

163
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,160
Less oil, less salt,

164
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:10,920
and no chili.

165
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,600
Thank you.

166
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,830
How about chrysanthemum tea for drinks?

167
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:19,800
It can reduce internal heat.

168
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,400
Chrysanthemum tea? Really?

169
00:07:21,410 --> 00:07:22,310
Just chrysanthemum tea, then.

170
00:07:22,310 --> 00:07:23,000
Chrysanthemum tea.

171
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,390
Alright.

172
00:07:23,390 --> 00:07:25,070
You're teasing me too?

173
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:27,270
I wouldn't dare.

174
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:28,560
You scared the hell out of me.

175
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,820
How are your injuries?

176
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:30,870
I'm heading to the hospital this afternoon

177
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:32,130
to visit You's mother.

178
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:33,240
Why don't you come with me

179
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:35,370
and have your injuries checked again?

180
00:07:37,159 --> 00:07:38,390
I'm fine.

181
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:39,510
Just flesh wounds.

182
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:40,800
No broken bones.

183
00:07:41,210 --> 00:07:42,360
Xiaolan told me everything.

184
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,850
She specifically asked me
to order light food for you,

185
00:07:43,850 --> 00:07:45,250
so I got you plain congee.

186
00:07:46,630 --> 00:07:47,290
You guys...

187
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:48,930
Don't be like this.

188
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,850
You're making me embarrassed.

189
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:52,920
Where are the two of them?

190
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:55,120
Parking the car. They'll be right here.

191
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,600
Thanks.

192
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:09,100
[Majestic Mahjong]

193
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,270
Boss.

194
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,430
What is it?

195
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:25,680
Why the panic?

196
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:27,920
About Bai Zhenzhu yesterday...

197
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,650
They reported it to the police.

198
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:36,270
What does that have to do with me?

199
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:38,200
After I left the restaurant yesterday,

200
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,460
I went to a karaoke bar.

201
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:40,720
After karaoke,

202
00:08:40,789 --> 00:08:41,990
I came straight here.

203
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,390
The owners of the karaoke,
the restaurant,

204
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:44,480
and even the street stalls

205
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,480
can all back me up.

206
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,120
So what if she reported it?

207
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,980
What the hell does it matter to me?

208
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:51,480
Let's go eat.

209
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,550
Have some of this.

210
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:12,750
Sis Bai.

211
00:09:13,230 --> 00:09:14,770
Eat. It's so light.

212
00:09:14,910 --> 00:09:15,440
Eat up.

213
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,880
Xiaolan, you were right.

214
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:21,770
I almost led everyone down the wrong path.

215
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:24,410
I got too carried away lately.

216
00:09:26,790 --> 00:09:27,750
Sis Bai, San,

217
00:09:28,410 --> 00:09:28,950
you didn't

218
00:09:28,950 --> 00:09:30,610
do anything illegal, did you?

219
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,400
No, we didn't.

220
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,480
And we never bullied

221
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,460
anyone either.

222
00:09:37,510 --> 00:09:38,200
But lately,

223
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,770
I've been leading my men

224
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:41,360
to go head-to-head with Ke Yixiong

225
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,690
and steal his business.

226
00:09:43,390 --> 00:09:45,590
Thinking about it now, I deserved this.

227
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,800
It was a wake-up call.

228
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,160
Because of me,

229
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:49,910
my fellow disciples have all gotten

230
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:51,910
caught up in this thrill of rivalry.

231
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:54,060
Now, I can still keep them in line.

232
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,550
But what if

233
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,150
one day I can't?

234
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:02,600
I still need to
lead everyone on the right path,

235
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,560
doing legitimate business.

236
00:10:05,870 --> 00:10:06,510
Sis Bai,

237
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:09,080
everyone acts on impulse sometimes.

238
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:09,910
The difference lies in

239
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:11,200
whether you can calm down

240
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:13,000
and truly deal with the problem.

241
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:15,140
It's good that you've figured it out.

242
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:17,940
Well, Xiaolan,

243
00:10:18,850 --> 00:10:19,980
you reminded me too.

244
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:22,840
I didn't think things through this time.

245
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,090
I acted on impulse.

246
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:28,480
San,

247
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:31,720
there's actually something about you
I really don't get.

248
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,510
Sis Bai and Ke Yixiong are

249
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:35,120
competing for turf and business—

250
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,550
that's to help her fellow disciples

251
00:10:36,550 --> 00:10:37,390
make a living.

252
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:38,240
Yes, yes.

253
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:40,910
But you... have your own business,

254
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:43,270
and you've got nothing to do
with Ke Yixiong.

255
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:44,510
You doing all this...

256
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:47,250
Why exactly did he do that?

257
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:48,670
Yeah, well...

258
00:10:49,140 --> 00:10:49,690
Why?

259
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,570
Yeah, why exactly?

260
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,960
When I first heard

261
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:54,100
that San went to Longcheng,

262
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:55,340
I was puzzled.

263
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,670
You see, San has weathered

264
00:10:56,670 --> 00:10:58,200
more storms than any of us.

265
00:10:58,390 --> 00:10:58,910
Logically,

266
00:10:58,910 --> 00:11:00,720
he should've been
more level-headed than us,

267
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,240
right? So, why?

268
00:11:02,910 --> 00:11:03,630
Yes, it's so strange.

269
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:04,910
Why did he do that? Why?

270
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:05,970
Why did you do that?

271
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:06,930
For Sis Zhenzhu!

272
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:15,960
I won't hide it anymore.

273
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:18,950
Sis Zhenzhu was bullied.

274
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,850
I just couldn't let that slide.

275
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,240
But last night,

276
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,970
Zhou Cheng asked me something.

277
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,080
If I got locked up

278
00:11:26,100 --> 00:11:26,730
over this,

279
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,270
we wouldn't be able to
face each other afterward—

280
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:30,730
how could I live with that?

281
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,540
I thought about it,

282
00:11:33,390 --> 00:11:34,650
and I couldn't bear it.

283
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:38,120
San,

284
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,240
what do you mean by that?

285
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:42,750
I couldn't bear the thought of...

286
00:11:42,750 --> 00:11:44,550
never seeing Sis Zhenzhu again.

287
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:50,690
Sis Zhenzhu,

288
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:51,870
I...

289
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:53,600
I...

290
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:56,120
I...

291
00:11:57,550 --> 00:11:58,120
I...

292
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:03,200
I still want to spar with you
in the future—

293
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,390
that move you taught me last time:

294
00:12:04,390 --> 00:12:05,520
the Bai Family Fist.

295
00:12:06,940 --> 00:12:09,370
San, are you serious?

296
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:09,910
Come on,

297
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:11,030
you can't be

298
00:12:11,030 --> 00:12:12,090
this dense, right?

299
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,080
Sis Zhenzhu, I like you.

300
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,480
I don't know how you feel.

301
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,320
I like you too.

302
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:45,750
That's great! That's great!

303
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:46,870
After all this time,

304
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:48,200
you two finally got it out

305
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:48,860
in the open!

306
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,000
You two were driving me crazy just now.

307
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:52,730
I almost stepped in to help him!

308
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:53,540
Come on.

309
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,270
A toast to love!

310
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,060
Come on!

311
00:12:57,150 --> 00:12:58,220
To love!

312
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,270
To love!

313
00:13:11,390 --> 00:13:12,020
Nurse,

314
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,150
please be gentle.

315
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:13,960
Thank you.

316
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:17,060
Changing the dressing doesn't hurt.

317
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,360
Be careful for the next few days,

318
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,510
and don't get the wounds wet.

319
00:13:20,510 --> 00:13:21,640
Keep taking the anti-inflammatory meds.

320
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:22,390
If you develop a fever

321
00:13:22,390 --> 00:13:23,150
or any other problems,

322
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:24,960
come back to the hospital immediately.

323
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,550
Nurse,

324
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:26,270
is there anything else

325
00:13:26,270 --> 00:13:27,440
we need to watch out for?

326
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,670
Please t-tell me everything.
I'll remember it all.

327
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:30,210
You

328
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,550
should make sure to protect her.

329
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:32,320
How did this happen?

330
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,600
She's black and blue all over.

331
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,440
Yes, yes.

332
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:37,300
I really didn't protect her well.

333
00:13:37,750 --> 00:13:39,410
Nurse Sun, come here a moment.

334
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:39,970
Coming.

335
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:41,170
All done.

336
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,910
Rest up, and then you're free to go.

337
00:13:42,910 --> 00:13:43,670
Thank you.

338
00:13:50,510 --> 00:13:52,110
Careful, don't catch a cold.

339
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:07,730
Sis Zhenzhu.

340
00:14:09,510 --> 00:14:10,440
I'm a rough man.

341
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:13,000
I'm not good with sweet talk.

342
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:16,720
And I'm not as good at business
or making money as you.

343
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:18,000
What I said earlier about protecting you—

344
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:18,790
that was me talking big.

345
00:14:18,730 --> 00:14:23,230
♪ I'm never tired by your side
during this long journey ♪

346
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,570
But I'll work hard at it!

347
00:14:23,710 --> 00:14:28,910
♪ We walk through
every leg of it together ♪

348
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:25,750
San.

349
00:14:26,910 --> 00:14:28,120
Actually, I don't need

350
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:29,320
anyone to protect me.

351
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:31,510
♪ As I climb over a peak ♪

352
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,120
What I want

353
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:33,550
is someone I can talk to

354
00:14:31,530 --> 00:14:34,110
♪ Another peak appears before my eyes ♪

355
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,150
in everyday life...

356
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:36,130
♪ Keep the goals high ♪

357
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:39,360
♪ Let your ideals always lead the way ♪

358
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:38,320
and a partner who can fight by my side

359
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,910
when danger comes.

360
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:42,050
♪ The road ahead is rough and steep ♪

361
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:41,480
You already are.

362
00:14:42,070 --> 00:14:44,720
♪ Yet we keep going ♪

363
00:14:44,970 --> 00:14:50,170
♪ May we embrace
both sorrow and joy in this life ♪

364
00:14:50,900 --> 00:14:52,830
♪ Moments of joy and sorrow ♪

365
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:52,750
Sis...

366
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:55,680
♪ Swirl around us ♪

367
00:14:53,510 --> 00:14:54,640
Why is your face red?

368
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,720
Ouch, ouch...

369
00:14:55,950 --> 00:14:57,050
♪ In the wind ♪

370
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:00,130
Sorry, sis.

371
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,440
Don't call me "Sis" anymore.

372
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:09,290
Call me Zhenzhu.

373
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:15,370
Zhenzhu.

374
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:17,630
San.

375
00:15:20,910 --> 00:15:21,440
Zhenzhu!

376
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:26,480
Li,

377
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:27,390
take a break.

378
00:15:27,390 --> 00:15:28,250
Come eat first.

379
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,670
I ordered all these for you.

380
00:15:29,670 --> 00:15:30,730
There are too many.

381
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:32,360
Two buns are enough for me.

382
00:15:32,880 --> 00:15:33,970
That won't do.

383
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:34,860
Give that to me.

384
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,000
Let me tell you,

385
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,510
you work so hard
to take care of your mom every day.

386
00:15:37,510 --> 00:15:39,040
You need proper nutrition.

387
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:41,030
Vegetables, meat, eggs—

388
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:42,200
you need them all.

389
00:15:42,330 --> 00:15:43,450
Only by eating well

390
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:45,360
will you have the strength
to take better care of your mom.

391
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:45,840
Eat up.

392
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:50,720
Come and eat too.

393
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:51,520
Stop working.

394
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:52,680
Coming, coming.

395
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,040
Is it good?

396
00:16:00,490 --> 00:16:01,420
It's delicious!

397
00:16:03,580 --> 00:16:04,600
I still want to hire a caregiver

398
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:05,390
for my mom.

399
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:06,630
Things at the Golden Sands Pool project

400
00:16:06,630 --> 00:16:07,760
are getting busier.

401
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,480
Even Ms. Xia

402
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,840
has to work overtime often.

403
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,960
As her assistant,

404
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:12,210
leaving on time every day

405
00:16:12,210 --> 00:16:13,740
doesn't feel appropriate.

406
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:16,070
Xiaolan won't mind.

407
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:18,900
Here's some water.

408
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,790
Ms. Xia hired an assistant

409
00:16:21,340 --> 00:16:22,670
precisely because she's too busy.

410
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:23,930
She's kind not to mind,

411
00:16:24,330 --> 00:16:25,080
but I can't be

412
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:26,140
oblivious to that.

413
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:28,470
Plus, with my family situation,

414
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:29,390
she still hired me

415
00:16:29,390 --> 00:16:30,790
and lent me money for my mom's treatment.

416
00:16:30,790 --> 00:16:32,390
I need to repay her kindness.

417
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:33,120
Besides,

418
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:34,840
I want to take on more work,

419
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,240
get a promotion and a raise soon,

420
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:36,910
and pay back

421
00:16:37,030 --> 00:16:38,830
the money I owe the company ASAP.

422
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:39,630
And then?

423
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:42,150
Then what?

424
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:44,200
Y-You're still so young

425
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:45,060
and so capable.

426
00:16:45,220 --> 00:16:46,720
You'll definitely make it big

427
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:47,630
and earn big money.

428
00:16:47,630 --> 00:16:48,570
Once you do,

429
00:16:48,670 --> 00:16:49,630
is there anything

430
00:16:49,630 --> 00:16:50,690
you dream of doing?

431
00:16:51,510 --> 00:16:53,310
Make it big and earn big money...

432
00:16:53,630 --> 00:16:54,320
I don't dare think

433
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,240
that far ahead.

434
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:57,910
I just hope

435
00:16:58,270 --> 00:16:59,000
I can give my mom

436
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:00,030
a good life.

437
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:01,840
When she wakes up,

438
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:03,700
I'll take her around Shengcheng.

439
00:17:03,910 --> 00:17:04,920
She hasn't really had a chance

440
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,349
to see the place properly.

441
00:17:06,349 --> 00:17:07,589
If there's a chance,

442
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:09,319
I want to take her to Hushi

443
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,300
and Jingcheng.

444
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:13,440
Kang Wei,

445
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:14,680
what's wrong?

446
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:18,310
Uh, nothing.

447
00:17:19,069 --> 00:17:20,030
I just think

448
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:22,270
you look really pretty when you smile.

449
00:17:22,270 --> 00:17:23,790
You should smile more often.

450
00:17:23,790 --> 00:17:25,400
A smile always lifts your spirits.

451
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,240
And when you're in good spirits,

452
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:27,440
life gets better too.

453
00:17:28,069 --> 00:17:29,480
What you said is really nice too.

454
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,480
You and your mom

455
00:17:30,750 --> 00:17:32,610
will definitely have a good life.

456
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:34,400
Hurry up and eat.

457
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:35,600
Let's eat. Let's eat.

458
00:17:36,550 --> 00:17:37,750
Here, have some meat.

459
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:40,070
I'll help myself.

460
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,130
Okay, okay, you eat it yourself.

461
00:17:41,130 --> 00:17:42,950
[Marriage Registration Office
of Shengcheng Civil Affairs Bureau]

462
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:48,800
Congratulations to you two.

463
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:01,460
Come on.

464
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:02,480
First of all,

465
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:04,290
I want to thank everyone

466
00:18:04,290 --> 00:18:04,970
for

467
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:07,230
all the help and support you've given me

468
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:08,370
and Comrade Liu Fen.

469
00:18:08,510 --> 00:18:10,030
And today, you've taken time

470
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:11,490
out of your busy schedules

471
00:18:11,790 --> 00:18:13,450
to come and celebrate with us.

472
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:14,570
From today onward,

473
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:16,110
we're a couple—

474
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:17,720
husband and wife—

475
00:18:17,750 --> 00:18:19,150
officially and legally.

476
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,030
Thank you, everyone!

477
00:18:21,030 --> 00:18:21,790
I'll down this glass.

478
00:18:21,790 --> 00:18:22,720
-Great!
-Great!

479
00:18:27,480 --> 00:18:28,200
He really drank it all!

480
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,550
We haven't clicked yet.

481
00:18:30,070 --> 00:18:31,030
From now on,

482
00:18:31,400 --> 00:18:32,690
my wife calls the shots.

483
00:18:32,690 --> 00:18:33,400
-See?
-Honey.

484
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,260
Learn from him.

485
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:35,160
Honey,

486
00:18:35,350 --> 00:18:36,720
do you want to say a few words?

487
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:37,590
Me?

488
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:39,400
Okay.

489
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:40,240
I'll say a few words.

490
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:40,640
Great.

491
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:43,350
We're all family here,

492
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:45,880
so I'm not afraid of
saying something wrong.

493
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,070
Actually, I have

494
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:49,400
so many things to say,

495
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:50,400
but

496
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:52,210
I don't know where to start.

497
00:18:53,510 --> 00:18:55,570
Many years ago, if someone had told me

498
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:58,590
that I could leave
that little village in Yunan

499
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:00,520
and come live in Shengcheng,

500
00:19:01,070 --> 00:19:02,130
that I could become

501
00:19:02,440 --> 00:19:04,240
the manager of a clothing store,

502
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:06,160
and marry someone

503
00:19:06,310 --> 00:19:07,960
as wonderful as Tang,

504
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:10,440
I wouldn't have dared to dream it—

505
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,240
it would've seemed like a fantasy!

506
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:13,550
But as time went on,

507
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:15,000
day by day,

508
00:19:16,030 --> 00:19:17,760
all of that actually came true.

509
00:19:18,110 --> 00:19:18,680
Fen,

510
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,310
that's not strange at all.

511
00:19:20,310 --> 00:19:21,750
You earned all of this through hard work—

512
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:22,610
you deserve it!

513
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:24,550
I just feel

514
00:19:24,550 --> 00:19:25,750
that I'm so lucky.

515
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:27,440
I'm truly so fortunate.

516
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:29,530
But I know in my heart

517
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:32,200
that I owe all of this

518
00:19:32,550 --> 00:19:34,640
to my family here

519
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:36,350
and friends.

520
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,640
It's you who have been helping me,

521
00:19:38,640 --> 00:19:39,970
helping Xiaolan and me.

522
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:42,640
First, I want to thank

523
00:19:43,310 --> 00:19:45,040
my brother and sister-in-law.

524
00:19:45,310 --> 00:19:46,720
If you hadn't

525
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:48,440
taken Xiaolan and me in back then,

526
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:50,440
we wouldn't have been able to get by.

527
00:19:51,550 --> 00:19:52,200
Thank you.

528
00:19:53,110 --> 00:19:53,480
Fen,

529
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:54,580
don't say that.

530
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:57,010
We're family. It goes without saying.

531
00:19:59,270 --> 00:20:01,110
I also want to thank Mr. Chen

532
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:02,900
for trusting me so much

533
00:20:03,070 --> 00:20:04,720
and putting me in charge of

534
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:05,580
Luna's stores.

535
00:20:05,590 --> 00:20:06,190
Thank you.

536
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:06,840
No, no, no.

537
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,120
You're being too formal.

538
00:20:08,120 --> 00:20:09,440
I've always believed work and friendship

539
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:10,480
are separate things.

540
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:11,540
You do your job well

541
00:20:11,590 --> 00:20:12,990
because you're capable.

542
00:20:13,590 --> 00:20:14,190
Thank you.

543
00:20:20,550 --> 00:20:21,610
I also want to thank

544
00:20:22,270 --> 00:20:23,070
Granny Yu!

545
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:26,590
We aren't related by blood.

546
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:28,270
I lost my parents

547
00:20:28,830 --> 00:20:29,790
at a young age,

548
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:32,510
so it was just my brother and me,

549
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,360
depending on each other.

550
00:20:35,030 --> 00:20:36,200
After meeting you,

551
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:38,880
you've always cared for me

552
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:40,010
with all your heart.

553
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:43,680
You always worried
I'd be taken advantage of

554
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:44,880
or suffer.

555
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:47,610
And you've always encouraged me.

556
00:20:48,030 --> 00:20:48,720
Actually,

557
00:20:49,270 --> 00:20:50,110
in my heart,

558
00:20:51,030 --> 00:20:52,750
you've long been my family.

559
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:57,640
I...

560
00:20:59,550 --> 00:21:00,400
Well,

561
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:04,070
t-that's all because your steamed buns

562
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:05,590
are delicious.

563
00:21:12,590 --> 00:21:14,110
And my daughter, Xiaolan.

564
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:16,760
I haven't been a good mother.

565
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:18,830
I have no great talents

566
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:21,840
and haven't been able to do much for you.

567
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:22,920
In the past,

568
00:21:23,440 --> 00:21:24,970
I caused you a lot of trouble

569
00:21:25,110 --> 00:21:26,350
and made you suffer.

570
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:30,240
You're the one who kept pulling me forward

571
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:31,370
to get us here today.

572
00:21:32,470 --> 00:21:33,310
My Xiaolan

573
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:35,270
is the best daughter

574
00:21:35,830 --> 00:21:36,830
in the world.

575
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:39,590
Mom,

576
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:41,030
don't say that.

577
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:42,440
Today isn't the time

578
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:43,970
to dwell on past hardships.

579
00:21:44,750 --> 00:21:46,640
It's time to look forward to the future.

580
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:47,750
I wish you and Uncle Tang

581
00:21:47,750 --> 00:21:49,010
an even better future!

582
00:21:50,310 --> 00:21:50,910
Thank you.

583
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:56,490
Finally,

584
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:59,050
I want to thank my Tang.

585
00:21:59,440 --> 00:22:00,750
You want to thank me too?

586
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:01,810
Then, pour me some.

587
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:05,480
Thank you for treating me so well

588
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,960
and for waiting for me to grow.

589
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:10,880
It was also you who made me realize that I

590
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:12,160
deserve to be loved

591
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:13,240
and to be happy.

592
00:22:14,790 --> 00:22:15,830
As for the rest...

593
00:22:17,240 --> 00:22:18,700
No need for all the thanks.

594
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,860
If there's anything more,

595
00:22:21,070 --> 00:22:21,590
Fen,

596
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,410
let's talk about it at home.

597
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:25,030
Come on!

598
00:22:25,310 --> 00:22:26,270
Come on!

599
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:28,520
We also need to thank the big boss

600
00:22:28,550 --> 00:22:29,310
and the big star here

601
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:30,160
for coming to join

602
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:31,360
our gathering today!

603
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:31,960
We're so honored!

604
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:32,640
Yong,

605
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:34,040
you're being too polite.

606
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:35,270
Here in Shengcheng,

607
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:36,310
we're all one family.

608
00:22:36,310 --> 00:22:37,000
That's right.

609
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:37,550
We're one family!

610
00:22:37,550 --> 00:22:38,310
We're family.

611
00:22:38,310 --> 00:22:39,310
Thank you, everyone!

612
00:22:39,310 --> 00:22:39,550
Cheers!

613
00:22:39,550 --> 00:22:40,630
Wishing you a happy marriage!

614
00:22:40,630 --> 00:22:42,680
-Congratulations!
-Congratulations.

615
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,000
And most importantly,

616
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:46,170
Fen was married off

617
00:22:46,190 --> 00:22:47,100
from my home.

618
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:48,510
Xiaolan,

619
00:22:49,480 --> 00:22:50,310
from now on,

620
00:22:50,360 --> 00:22:51,960
this is your natal home, too.

621
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:52,840
Great.

622
00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:55,570
Cheers.

623
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:56,590
To another home.

624
00:22:56,590 --> 00:22:57,480
-Cheers.
-Great!

625
00:22:57,480 --> 00:22:59,280
-Thank you, everyone!
-Cheers!

626
00:23:17,110 --> 00:23:17,970
Mom, it's fine.

627
00:23:18,310 --> 00:23:19,440
It's not far anyway.

628
00:23:19,830 --> 00:23:20,890
Come back anytime.

629
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:23,810
When I have time,

630
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:26,640
I'll come back
and cook you something nice.

631
00:23:28,070 --> 00:23:28,600
Let's go.

632
00:23:28,830 --> 00:23:30,290
I'll walk you downstairs.

633
00:23:43,070 --> 00:23:43,960
Okay, let's put it in together.

634
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:44,310
Okay.

635
00:23:45,350 --> 00:23:46,270
It's a bit heavy.

636
00:23:46,270 --> 00:23:47,330
Easy. Put it there.

637
00:23:51,270 --> 00:23:52,530
Take care of yourself.

638
00:23:53,110 --> 00:23:54,040
Come back often.

639
00:23:56,250 --> 00:23:56,790
Goodbye, Auntie.

640
00:23:56,790 --> 00:23:57,650
We're off then.

641
00:23:58,110 --> 00:23:58,750
Bye, Mom.

642
00:23:58,960 --> 00:24:00,290
Let's go. Get in the car.

643
00:24:22,010 --> 00:24:23,070
What are you dawdling around for?

644
00:24:23,070 --> 00:24:24,160
What are you looking at?

645
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:25,290
Hurry up and load it!

646
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:27,590
They're waiting for
the delivery over there!

647
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:28,310
My wife.

648
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:30,250
What do you mean, "your wife"?

649
00:24:30,450 --> 00:24:31,200
Even if it were your mother,

650
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:33,240
you still have to stack the goods for me!
Hurry up!

651
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:35,170
We need to get these delivered now!

652
00:24:48,830 --> 00:24:49,480
Xia Dajun,

653
00:24:50,210 --> 00:24:51,550
if you keep dawdling like this,

654
00:24:51,550 --> 00:24:53,450
I'll find someone else
to make the delivery!

655
00:24:53,450 --> 00:24:54,510
Can you do it or not?

656
00:25:00,070 --> 00:25:01,160
Let's have some herbal tea.

657
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:01,510
Okay.

658
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:03,600
Ma'am,

659
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:05,210
two cups of 24 Herbs tea.

660
00:25:05,210 --> 00:25:06,140
Coming right up.

661
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:12,340
Here are your herbal teas.

662
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:13,970
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

663
00:25:18,510 --> 00:25:19,590
I didn't expect

664
00:25:20,070 --> 00:25:20,880
my mom to get married

665
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:21,680
before me.

666
00:25:23,960 --> 00:25:24,760
What's wrong?

667
00:25:25,510 --> 00:25:26,910
Feeling a bit emotional?

668
00:25:27,590 --> 00:25:28,510
Or...

669
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:30,840
are you missing your own mom?

670
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:33,730
Zhou Cheng,

671
00:25:34,920 --> 00:25:36,110
actually, I rarely

672
00:25:36,110 --> 00:25:37,370
think of them anymore.

673
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:39,000
Sometimes,

674
00:25:39,590 --> 00:25:41,310
I've completely come to see Liu Fen

675
00:25:41,310 --> 00:25:42,550
as my own mom.

676
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:45,830
All that childhood longing for a mother

677
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:47,030
that had nowhere to go

678
00:25:47,110 --> 00:25:48,840
finally has somewhere to land.

679
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:53,160
That must be a blessing for

680
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:55,290
both you and Auntie Liu.

681
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:58,070
But...

682
00:25:58,510 --> 00:25:59,440
sometimes,

683
00:26:00,550 --> 00:26:01,950
I still secretly wonder.

684
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:03,350
I wonder...

685
00:26:05,350 --> 00:26:06,880
if my own mom and dad

686
00:26:07,350 --> 00:26:07,960
saw you,

687
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:10,060
what would their reaction be?

688
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:12,420
Would they be like Liu Fen,

689
00:26:12,530 --> 00:26:13,400
seeing her son-in-law

690
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:14,730
as perfect in every way?

691
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,290
Or would they be like

692
00:26:16,350 --> 00:26:17,920
my uncle and Uncle Tang,

693
00:26:18,350 --> 00:26:19,310
feeling like their precious daughter

694
00:26:19,310 --> 00:26:20,640
got "snatched by a pig"?

695
00:26:23,070 --> 00:26:23,510
Well,

696
00:26:24,120 --> 00:26:24,980
now I'm the pig.

697
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:26,680
I'll take it.

698
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:27,750
Still better than

699
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:30,320
being compared to
cow dung next to a flower.

700
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:34,490
Xiaolan.

701
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:36,830
I think

702
00:26:37,590 --> 00:26:38,720
your mom and dad

703
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,530
might have already seen us.

704
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:43,270
Look.

705
00:26:44,350 --> 00:26:45,350
The world

706
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:47,490
is such a mysterious place.

707
00:26:47,750 --> 00:26:48,310
Maybe

708
00:26:48,310 --> 00:26:49,790
in some other dimension,

709
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:52,370
they've already seen everything.

710
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:56,270
Mom, Dad,

711
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:58,480
if you can see me,

712
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:00,970
you must be happy with

713
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:02,530
who I've become now, right?

714
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:18,450
So, do you think

715
00:27:18,550 --> 00:27:20,550
this part needs to be revised again?

716
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:22,200
I think we still need to upgrade

717
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:22,800
this part.

718
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:23,590
This part?

719
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:24,480
Okay. I'll...

720
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:25,640
Ms. Xia, are you having a date

721
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:26,440
in the office?

722
00:27:27,310 --> 00:27:28,310
Watch your image.

723
00:27:28,400 --> 00:27:29,440
I'm consulting Mr. Zhou

724
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:30,510
on a legal matter.

725
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:32,010
Do you need something?

726
00:27:33,030 --> 00:27:33,790
I'm just worried you might be

727
00:27:33,790 --> 00:27:35,450
neglecting work, that's all.

728
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:36,640
Here.

729
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:38,070
This is the marketing plan

730
00:27:38,070 --> 00:27:38,920
for Electronics City.

731
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:39,880
I've reviewed it.

732
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:41,270
There are no legal risks.

733
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:41,750
Mr. Du, you can

734
00:27:41,750 --> 00:27:43,010
proceed with the plan.

735
00:27:43,920 --> 00:27:44,750
Ms. Xia...

736
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:47,610
aren't you going to help me with it?

737
00:27:48,110 --> 00:27:48,920
Du Zhaohui,

738
00:27:49,430 --> 00:27:50,790
you paid the consultation fee,

739
00:27:50,790 --> 00:27:51,550
and I gave you the idea

740
00:27:51,550 --> 00:27:52,750
of Electronics City.

741
00:27:52,790 --> 00:27:54,550
That was already more than sufficient.

742
00:27:54,550 --> 00:27:55,660
This marketing plan

743
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:56,860
is already a bonus.

744
00:27:57,070 --> 00:27:58,200
If you want anything else,

745
00:27:58,200 --> 00:27:59,660
I'll have to charge extra.

746
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,400
Even if you wanted to charge me now,

747
00:28:01,400 --> 00:28:02,260
I couldn't pay.

748
00:28:03,160 --> 00:28:04,410
Let me give you an update—

749
00:28:04,410 --> 00:28:05,440
the interior build-out of

750
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:07,000
Electronics City is almost done.

751
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,130
We can open anytime.

752
00:28:08,310 --> 00:28:09,070
What do you think—

753
00:28:09,070 --> 00:28:10,030
should we pick an auspicious day

754
00:28:10,030 --> 00:28:10,790
to open now?

755
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:14,640
Your father is going to
announce the results

756
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:16,040
at his birthday banquet.

757
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:18,860
Let's make it three days
before the banquet.

758
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:19,550
Three days?

759
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:21,750
How much can we make in just three days?

760
00:28:21,750 --> 00:28:23,160
And 30 days—so what?

761
00:28:23,750 --> 00:28:24,480
Trust me.

762
00:28:24,750 --> 00:28:25,440
Your father

763
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:27,110
won't just look at the immediate figures.

764
00:28:27,110 --> 00:28:27,960
He will also look at

765
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:29,290
future profitability.

766
00:28:30,270 --> 00:28:30,830
Fine.

767
00:28:31,030 --> 00:28:33,350
I'll trust your judgment, Ms. Xia.

768
00:28:35,310 --> 00:28:36,040
Well then...

769
00:28:36,940 --> 00:28:37,870
I'm heading out.

770
00:28:38,780 --> 00:28:40,180
Do you want to walk me out?

771
00:28:47,240 --> 00:28:47,840
Oh, right.

772
00:28:48,440 --> 00:28:51,030
There's been progress
on the smuggling case lately.

773
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:53,270
I might've... misunderstood Du Zhaohui.

774
00:28:53,270 --> 00:28:54,160
He really hasn't been involved

775
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:55,750
in his family's business for a long time.

776
00:28:55,750 --> 00:28:57,350
Do you remember that he once said

777
00:28:57,350 --> 00:28:59,000
Xia Dajun saved his life?

778
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:01,190
At that time, someone really did

779
00:29:01,190 --> 00:29:02,650
try to take revenge on him.

780
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:03,720
The Du family,

781
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:05,400
for the sake of smuggling profits,

782
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:07,330
wouldn't even spare their own son.

783
00:29:07,510 --> 00:29:09,030
That's not necessarily true.

784
00:29:09,030 --> 00:29:10,880
The people weren't sent by Du Chengrong.

785
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:12,410
Du Chengrong has two wives,

786
00:29:12,510 --> 00:29:13,840
countless mistresses,

787
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,560
and illegitimate children.

788
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:18,200
The Du family

789
00:29:18,640 --> 00:29:20,030
might be far messier

790
00:29:20,310 --> 00:29:21,240
than it appears.

791
00:29:22,750 --> 00:29:24,160
Born into such a family,

792
00:29:25,120 --> 00:29:26,320
no wonder Du Zhaohui

793
00:29:26,350 --> 00:29:27,750
never plays by the rules.

794
00:29:35,790 --> 00:29:37,920
I still get butterflies when I see her.

795
00:29:41,350 --> 00:29:42,680
Go straight to the port.

796
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:44,070
Let's go back to Gangdao.

797
00:29:44,070 --> 00:29:44,640
Young Master,

798
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:46,900
you had a golf appointment with Mr. Tang.

799
00:29:47,440 --> 00:29:48,440
What golf?

800
00:29:49,510 --> 00:29:50,110
Xia Xiaolan has come up with

801
00:29:50,110 --> 00:29:51,310
so many clever ideas.

802
00:29:52,070 --> 00:29:54,200
Someone has to help her make them happen.

803
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:56,030
Otherwise, my money would be wasted.

804
00:29:56,030 --> 00:29:56,790
If I remember correctly,

805
00:29:56,790 --> 00:29:57,830
Young Master, that check

806
00:29:57,830 --> 00:29:59,270
seems to be a dud.

807
00:29:59,850 --> 00:30:01,760
Do I need you to remind me? Just drive.

808
00:30:01,760 --> 00:30:03,490
I was only trying to be helpful.

809
00:30:07,320 --> 00:30:11,390
[Gangdao]

810
00:30:13,480 --> 00:30:15,000
Young Master! Young Master!

811
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:15,650
I found it.

812
00:30:15,680 --> 00:30:16,480
Mr. Chen's company

813
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:17,940
is right in this building.

814
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,040
After all these years,

815
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:20,770
Chen is still

816
00:30:20,790 --> 00:30:22,200
stuck in this dump.

817
00:30:22,270 --> 00:30:23,640
How's he supposed to do big business here?

818
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:24,480
Drive. Let's go.

819
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:24,810
Okay.

820
00:30:29,160 --> 00:30:30,200
Second Young Master!

821
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:30,960
Du Zhaoji!

822
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:48,790
Weird.

823
00:30:49,030 --> 00:30:50,230
Why is Du Zhaoji here?

824
00:30:51,030 --> 00:30:51,830
He didn't look this way, did he?

825
00:30:51,830 --> 00:30:52,760
No, no, no.

826
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:53,240
Relax.

827
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,920
The Second Young Master looks

828
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:57,270
even more afraid of
running into acquaintances than you do.

829
00:30:57,270 --> 00:30:59,400
But he studied abroad from a young age.

830
00:31:00,010 --> 00:31:00,680
How could he have

831
00:31:00,680 --> 00:31:02,680
friends living in a place like this?

832
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:21,480
Ms. Xia, here is the room key.

833
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:22,610
Please keep it safe.

834
00:31:22,880 --> 00:31:24,640
The room is on the third floor.
This is the room number.

835
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:25,970
Stay here for a few days.

836
00:31:26,200 --> 00:31:28,130
Someone will come looking for you.

837
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:40,040
Sorry. Sorry.

838
00:31:40,350 --> 00:31:41,400
I didn't mean to.

839
00:31:41,550 --> 00:31:43,110
P-Please spare me.

840
00:31:47,760 --> 00:31:48,690
Raise your head.

841
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:58,920
So tacky.

842
00:32:00,590 --> 00:32:01,680
Give me a way out!

843
00:32:01,960 --> 00:32:03,030
I'll do anything!

844
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:14,530
Could it be that my plan actually worked?

845
00:32:16,110 --> 00:32:17,960
Du Zhaohui, oh, Du Zhaohui,

846
00:32:18,270 --> 00:32:19,640
you really are a genius.

847
00:32:20,750 --> 00:32:21,280
Let's go.

848
00:32:22,780 --> 00:32:24,880
As for the interior design of the theater,

849
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:26,200
I want the audience

850
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:28,260
to have a more immersive experience.

851
00:32:28,510 --> 00:32:29,030
So,

852
00:32:29,920 --> 00:32:31,510
I want to use the concept of a starry sky

853
00:32:31,510 --> 00:32:33,310
as the theme for this design.

854
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:35,550
-When the lights go out...
-Ms. Xia.

855
00:32:35,550 --> 00:32:36,790
There's a call for you.

856
00:32:36,790 --> 00:32:37,960
When I'm studying with Mr. Mao,

857
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:38,950
I don't take calls.

858
00:32:38,950 --> 00:32:40,590
It's from Ms. Ye.

859
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:42,610
She said she's
returning to Gangdao tonight

860
00:32:42,610 --> 00:32:44,740
and wants to see you before she leaves.

861
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,270
Ms. Ye?

862
00:32:53,070 --> 00:32:54,000
I thought

863
00:32:54,350 --> 00:32:55,680
we wouldn't meet again.

864
00:32:58,350 --> 00:32:59,830
I was rather rude last time.

865
00:32:59,830 --> 00:33:01,230
I hope you can forgive me.

866
00:33:02,830 --> 00:33:04,160
Here, give me your bowl.

867
00:33:05,310 --> 00:33:07,160
I know you're from Esheng.

868
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:09,240
The last time I went to Jiangcheng
for a meeting,

869
00:33:09,240 --> 00:33:10,900
I really liked the food there.

870
00:33:11,120 --> 00:33:11,680
I'm not sure

871
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:13,240
