873
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:15,560
Try some.

874
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:16,750
Here.

875
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:25,590
You're still the same as

876
00:33:25,590 --> 00:33:26,860
