880
00:33:39,600 --> 00:33:40,760
There was so much

881
00:33:40,790 --> 00:33:42,390
I didn't get to say last time.

882
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:43,920
But after I went back,

883
00:33:44,310 --> 00:33:45,400
I thought a lot.

884
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:48,080
If it weren't for you,

885
00:33:48,270 --> 00:33:49,930
I wouldn't be where I am today.

886
00:33:50,070 --> 00:33:51,530
So I invited you here today

887
00:33:51,830 --> 00:33:52,790
to tell you that

888
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:55,280
even though Du Zhaoji is my boss,

889
00:33:55,830 --> 00:33:56,830
regarding

890
00:33:56,830 --> 00:33:57,690
your kindness,

891
00:33:58,070 --> 00:33:59,000
I, Ye Xiaoqiong,

892
00:33:59,240 --> 00:33:59,970
will repay it

893
00:34:00,480 --> 00:34:01,590
many times over!

894
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:05,560
Let's eat.

895
00:34:07,110 --> 00:34:08,000
Ye Xiaoqiong

896
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:09,590
