897
00:34:09,590 --> 00:34:11,280
Isn't she afraid her boss, Du Zhaoji,

898
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,440
will get suspicious?

899
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:14,320
The fact that she came to
see me so openly

900
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:15,100
shows

901
00:34:15,120 --> 00:34:16,960
Du Zhaoji has complete confidence

902
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,150
