903
00:34:18,150 --> 00:34:19,280
But that confidence

904
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:21,280
definitely isn't born of friendship.

905
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:22,540
It's because Du Zhaoji

906
00:34:22,590 --> 00:34:24,400
has something on Ye Xiaoqiong.

907
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:26,510
I'm guessing Ye Xiaoqiong's revenge

908
00:34:26,510 --> 00:34:27,230
relied on

909
00:34:27,230 --> 00:34:28,290
Du Zhaoji's power.

910
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:31,330
Ye Xiaoqiong really jumped

911
00:34:31,520 --> 00:34:33,650
out of the frying pan and into the fire.

912
00:34:34,449 --> 00:34:35,370
Ye Xiaoqiong

913
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:36,710
is no longer the pushover

914
00:34:36,710 --> 00:34:38,110
we met back then.

915
00:34:38,710 --> 00:34:40,150
The fact that she's managed to
secure a place

916
00:34:40,150 --> 00:34:40,900
by Du Zhaoji's side

917
00:34:40,900 --> 00:34:42,400
shows she's extraordinary.

918
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:43,460
But no matter what,

919
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:45,030
I still hope she can

920
00:34:45,030 --> 00:34:46,090
get what she wants.

921
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:48,480
No one in the Du family

922
00:34:48,480 --> 00:34:49,610
is easy to deal with.

923
00:34:50,070 --> 00:34:50,960
All that can be found

924
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:52,150
about Du Zhaoji is

925
00:34:52,170 --> 00:34:54,690
