since middle school.

926
00:34:55,190 --> 00:34:56,190
After returning,

927
00:34:56,190 --> 00:34:57,960
he's been working for the family business.

928
00:34:57,960 --> 00:34:59,280
His style

929
00:34:59,280 --> 00:35:00,280
is indeed very much like

930
00:35:00,280 --> 00:35:02,000
that of a traditional business elite.

931
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:03,000
He's also well regarded

932
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:04,200
