933
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:06,110
In this competition with Du Zhaohui,

934
00:35:06,110 --> 00:35:07,320
he's chosen the manufacturing sector.

935
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:08,030
He even acquired a production line

936
00:35:08,030 --> 00:35:09,480
in Southeast Asia.

937
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,930
He really has a knack for business.

938
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:16,070
However, compared to the concept
of Electronics City,

939
00:35:16,070 --> 00:35:18,670
he still lacks
a bit of foresight and boldness.

940
00:35:19,480 --> 00:35:19,880
Well,

941
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:21,000
of course.

942
00:35:21,420 --> 00:35:22,360
Electronics City

943
00:35:22,360 --> 00:35:23,910
has you as its strategist

944
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,800
from the future.

945
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:26,960
What?

946
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:29,630
You mean my only strengths

947
00:35:29,630 --> 00:35:31,550
are prediction and a "cheat code"?

948
00:35:31,550 --> 00:35:32,360
Of course not.

949
00:35:33,510 --> 00:35:35,000
I mean,

950
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:36,480
that's just

951
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:38,710
