954
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:43,490
But only I know them.

955
00:35:43,570 --> 00:35:44,260
Really?

956
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:46,070
Well, if you don't list

957
00:35:46,070 --> 00:35:47,400
