958
00:35:47,590 --> 00:35:48,650
I'll throw you off.

959
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:51,220
Then I'll do it.

960
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:54,510
Here—one, two, three, four, five.

961
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:55,880
Down you go.

962
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:56,810
[Asia's No. 1—Shengcheng
Chengrong Electronics City Plaza—]

963
00:35:56,810 --> 00:35:57,740
[50 Days to Grand Opening]

964
00:36:02,350 --> 00:36:04,180
Back when we opened Luna,

965
00:36:03,970 --> 00:36:07,980
[Luna]

966
