967
00:36:05,550 --> 00:36:07,000
Otherwise, I would've run an ad
like this too—

968
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:07,860
30 days in a row.

969
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:09,150
Luna's ads cost

970
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:10,670
