977
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:19,850
are selling for.

978
00:36:20,040 --> 00:36:20,960
Rent only, not for sale.

979
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,150
If you sign now,

980
00:36:22,150 --> 00:36:23,840
