981
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:25,190
He needs to hurry if he wants one.

982
00:36:25,190 --> 00:36:26,190
The prime spots in the first batch

983
00:36:26,190 --> 00:36:27,140
have already been snapped up.

984
00:36:27,140 --> 00:36:28,670
And there aren't many left.

985
00:36:28,930 --> 00:36:29,810
Really?

986
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,230
Your stalls are that popular?

987
00:36:31,230 --> 00:36:32,760
When have I ever lied to you?

988
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:39,550
Hurry up!

989
00:36:41,360 --> 00:36:42,510
So slow!

990
00:36:42,020 --> 00:36:43,290
[Chengrong Electronics City—
Prime Stalls Now Open for Leasing]

991
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,230
Do you even know the rules?

992
00:36:47,230 --> 00:36:48,150
Get to the back of the line!

993
00:36:48,150 --> 00:36:49,110
Miss, can I squeeze in?

994
00:36:49,110 --> 00:36:50,150
No cuts!

995
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:51,360
The mall is so big,

996
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:53,480
and there are so many stalls!
They won't run out!

997
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:54,550
With so many stalls,

998
00:36:54,550 --> 00:36:55,590
why not release them all at once?

999
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:56,960
Why split them into three batches?

1000
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:57,630
I wonder which

1001
00:36:57,630 --> 00:36:59,360
wicked bastard came up
with this dirty trick!

1002
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:00,230
Can you hurry up?

1003
00:37:00,230 --> 00:37:00,710
Exactly!

1004
00:37:00,710 --> 00:37:02,370
What's wrong with you people?

1005
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:03,670
The annual rent

1006
00:37:03,670 --> 00:37:04,710
will bring in seven million,

1007
00:37:04,710 --> 00:37:06,360
and it takes up such a huge area.

1008
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:07,840
It'll keep generating profit

1009
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:08,970
for decades to come.

1010
00:37:09,930 --> 00:37:10,880
How can that Brat Ji

1011
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:11,940
even compare to me?

1012
00:37:12,110 --> 00:37:13,630
If everything goes smoothly

1013
00:37:13,630 --> 00:37:15,150
and continues like this,

1014
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:17,650
the Second Master Du might actually lose.

1015
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:19,170
There's only one month left.

1016
00:37:19,170 --> 00:37:21,230
How is he supposed to turn the tables?

1017
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:22,130
Xia Xiaolan,

1018
00:37:22,230 --> 00:37:22,920
do you know what people here

1019
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:24,120
are saying about you?

1020
00:37:24,770 --> 00:37:25,330
They say,

1021
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:26,380
"Which wicked bastard came up with

1022
00:37:26,380 --> 00:37:28,640
this dirty trick?"

1023
00:37:31,510 --> 00:37:32,280
Du Zhaohui,

1024
00:37:32,630 --> 00:37:33,920
right now, you look just like

1025
00:37:33,920 --> 00:37:35,190
those villains in the movies.

1026
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:36,720
Don't say I didn't warn you—

1027
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:38,190
villains always die

1028
00:37:38,190 --> 00:37:39,510
because they celebrate too early.

1029
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:40,920
Never mind
that there's still a month left—

1030
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:42,410
even if there were only one day left,

1031
00:37:42,410 --> 00:37:43,150
as long as Du Chengrong

1032
00:37:43,150 --> 00:37:44,360
hasn't announced the winner,

1033
00:37:44,360 --> 00:37:45,190
Du Zhaoji

1034
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:47,610
still has a chance to turn this around.

1035
00:37:48,030 --> 00:37:49,440
I'd like to see him try.

1036
00:37:49,870 --> 00:37:51,200
Don't worry. It's fine.

1037
00:37:57,030 --> 00:37:57,440
Hello?

1038
00:38:02,070 --> 00:38:02,630
Where did this man, Nie Weiguo,

1039
00:38:02,630 --> 00:38:03,510
come from?

1040
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:07,440
He's claiming that our Electronics City
design copied his work!

1041
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:08,710
Judging by the lawyer's letter,

1042
00:38:08,710 --> 00:38:09,970
that is what he thinks.

1043
00:38:10,320 --> 00:38:11,250
What do you mean?

1044
00:38:11,670 --> 00:38:12,590
Is there more to it

1045
00:38:12,590 --> 00:38:13,650
beyond the letter?

1046
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:15,800
Everything requires evidence.

1047
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,110
For example, if I draw

1048
00:38:17,110 --> 00:38:18,370
a colored apple first,

1049
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:19,110
and then you draw one,

1050
00:38:19,110 --> 00:38:20,320
that's you copying me.

1051
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:21,980
But if the timeline is unclear

1052
00:38:22,110 --> 00:38:23,760
and you run over, claiming I copied you,

1053
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:25,490
people might still believe it.

1054
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:28,000
We're done for. We're done for.

1055
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:29,810
Stop saying we're done for.

1056
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,880
It's my own work.

1057
00:38:31,150 --> 00:38:33,460
I know perfectly well
whether I copied or not.

1058
00:38:33,460 --> 00:38:35,910
The key is the timeline.

1059
00:38:36,190 --> 00:38:37,880
Nie Weiguo claims

1060
00:38:38,150 --> 00:38:39,630
that Hou Qi saw

1061
00:38:39,630 --> 00:38:41,630
his unpublished design drawings.

1062
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:42,590
Me?

1063
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:43,510
How is that possible?

1064
00:38:43,510 --> 00:38:44,550
I left Jiangcheng Design Institute

1065
00:38:44,550 --> 00:38:45,440
ages ago!

1066
00:38:49,710 --> 00:38:51,170
Hou Qi, come here for a sec.

1067
00:39:01,480 --> 00:39:02,710
Is it really this woman?

1068
00:39:02,710 --> 00:39:03,440
Impossible.

1069
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:05,510
Ms. Hou Qi isn't that kind of person.

1070
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:05,960
Wait,

1071
00:39:06,190 --> 00:39:07,190
weren't most of the exterior designs

1072
00:39:07,190 --> 00:39:08,110
Ms. Xia's work?

1073
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:09,070
What does this have to do

1074
00:39:09,070 --> 00:39:09,930
with Ms. Hou Qi?

1075
00:39:10,110 --> 00:39:11,240
What are you saying?

1076
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:13,030
How could Ms. Xia possibly plagiarize?

1077
00:39:13,030 --> 00:39:13,440
Yeah.

1078
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:14,550
Ms. Xia,

1079
00:39:14,950 --> 00:39:17,210
I swear I absolutely did not plagiarize.

1080
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,170
Don't worry.

1081
00:39:18,550 --> 00:39:19,950
Of course, I believe you.

1082
00:39:20,150 --> 00:39:21,280
I just want to ask—

1083
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:22,760
what kind of person is

1084
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,890
Nie Weiguo exactly?

1085
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:27,880
That guy, Nie,

1086
00:39:28,650 --> 00:39:29,500
is a scumbag.

1087
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:32,530
Back then, he stole my work,

1088
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,260
exploited my labor...

1089
00:39:35,430 --> 00:39:36,960
and even got handsy with me.

1090
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:38,670
I couldn't take it anymore,

1091
00:39:38,670 --> 00:39:39,630
and that's why I quit

1092
00:39:39,630 --> 00:39:41,090
and even left Jiangcheng.

1093
00:39:41,750 --> 00:39:42,510
I can't believe this guy

1094
00:39:42,510 --> 00:39:44,510
is getting more and more shameless.

1095
00:39:46,840 --> 00:39:47,900
I'm sorry, Ms. Xia.

1096
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:49,780
No matter what,

1097
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:51,190
this trouble started

1098
00:39:51,190 --> 00:39:52,000
because of me.

1099
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:53,590
Bad people do bad things.

1100
00:39:53,590 --> 00:39:55,110
What does this have to do with you?

1101
00:39:55,110 --> 00:39:55,880
Don't try to take it all

1102
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:56,920
upon yourself.

1103
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:58,220
Attorney Zhou,

1104
00:39:58,590 --> 00:40:00,800
you can't just
accuse someone of plagiarism, right?

1105
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:03,030
Surely the law needs something
to go on, right?

1106
00:40:03,030 --> 00:40:03,830
The evidence.

1107
00:40:04,140 --> 00:40:04,940
Do we have any?

1108
00:40:05,030 --> 00:40:05,440
Yes.

1109
00:40:06,670 --> 00:40:07,630
But...

1110
00:40:08,280 --> 00:40:09,110
But what?

1111
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:12,360
Is this going to be a tough case?

1112
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:14,280
The fact that Nie Weiguo

1113
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:15,070
has made this public

1114
00:40:15,070 --> 00:40:17,000
shows he won't let it drop quietly.

1115
00:40:17,440 --> 00:40:18,280
He's just a deputy director

1116
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:20,190
at a small design institute—

1117
00:40:20,510 --> 00:40:22,170
what kind of waves can he make?

1118
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:24,030
I'll figure something out

1119
00:40:24,030 --> 00:40:25,160
and make some calls.

1120
00:40:25,670 --> 00:40:27,200
Get back to work, everyone.

1121
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:30,960
I'm certain this whole thing

1122
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:31,670
was cooked up

1123
00:40:31,670 --> 00:40:32,880
by that Brat Ji!

1124
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:34,550
That darn bastard!

1125
00:40:36,630 --> 00:40:38,670
Du Zhaohui thinks

1126
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:40,000
Du Zhaoji is behind this

1127
00:40:40,030 --> 00:40:41,490
and that it's aimed at him.

1128
00:40:42,190 --> 00:40:43,190
What do you think?

1129
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:45,030
For now,

1130
00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:47,040
it does look that way.

1131
00:40:47,590 --> 00:40:48,230
But...

1132
00:40:49,030 --> 00:40:50,760
But something still feels off.

1133
00:40:50,780 --> 00:40:52,730
Even though Chengrong Group

1134
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:53,840
will be affected,

1135
00:40:54,150 --> 00:40:55,410
the biggest victim...

1136
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:56,820
is actually me.

1137
00:40:57,880 --> 00:40:59,340
Then that can only mean...

1138
00:40:59,630 --> 00:41:01,030
Xia Ziyu is involved too.

1139
00:41:02,560 --> 00:41:04,510
But whether it's Du Zhaoji

1140
00:41:04,510 --> 00:41:05,710
or Xia Ziyu,

1141
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:07,280
don't you think they seem to know you

1142
00:41:07,280 --> 00:41:08,010
far too well?

1143
00:41:08,920 --> 00:41:10,070
Your grudge with Nie Weiguo

1144
00:41:10,070 --> 00:41:11,880
started as recently as

1145
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:13,190
the Jiangcheng Architecture Symposium.

1146
00:41:13,190 --> 00:41:14,630
Even an enemy this far away,

1147
00:41:14,630 --> 00:41:16,710
and yet they still managed to
track him down through Hou Qi.

1148
00:41:16,710 --> 00:41:17,670
Unless...

1149
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:22,150
Unless there is a mole close to me.

1150
00:41:30,840 --> 00:41:32,040
Who do you think it is?

1151
00:41:32,550 --> 00:41:33,110
Hou Qi?

1152
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:34,700
It can't be her.

1153
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:36,030
Before Nie Weiguo and I

1154
00:41:36,030 --> 00:41:37,150
even crossed paths,

1155
00:41:37,150 --> 00:41:38,000
she had already left

1156
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,040
the Jiangcheng Design Institute.

1157
00:41:39,040 --> 00:41:39,560
It shows

1158
00:41:39,590 --> 00:41:41,050
that she did resign for personal reasons

1159
00:41:41,050 --> 00:41:43,380
and had nothing to do
with what came after.

1160
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:45,220
Then who do you think it is?

1161
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:47,300
You should be able to guess

1162
00:41:47,630 --> 00:41:48,760
who I'm thinking of.

1163
00:41:54,630 --> 00:41:55,510
But he...

1164
00:41:56,940 --> 00:41:57,920
hasn't shown anything unusual lately.

1165
00:41:57,920 --> 00:41:58,340
True.

1166
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:00,150
We don't have

1167
00:42:00,150 --> 00:42:01,880
any concrete evidence at the moment.

1168
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:04,030
But regarding the incident
at the symposium

1169
00:42:04,030 --> 00:42:05,320
and Hou Qi's situation,

1170
00:42:05,320 --> 00:42:07,050
he's the one who knows the most.

1171
00:42:07,960 --> 00:42:09,630
Personally, I don't want to believe

1172
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:10,360
he could betray us

1173
00:42:10,360 --> 00:42:11,440
like that.

1174
00:42:12,070 --> 00:42:13,930
So let's just wait and see for now.

1175
00:42:16,070 --> 00:42:17,710
What worries me most is—

1176
00:42:18,190 --> 00:42:19,230
if Xia Ziyu really

1177
00:42:19,670 --> 00:42:20,880
is behind all this,

1178
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:21,960
there will

1179
00:42:22,190 --> 00:42:23,070
almost certainly be

1180
00:42:23,070 --> 00:42:24,530
more dirty tricks to come.

1181
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:26,550
I think the color of the section

1182
00:42:26,550 --> 00:42:27,920
could be brighter.

1183
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:28,920
To make it stand out more.

1184
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:29,280
Okay.

1185
00:42:29,300 --> 00:42:29,760
Listen,

1186
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:30,760
go find Hou Qi.

1187
00:42:30,960 --> 00:42:32,000
I talked to her about it yesterday.

1188
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:32,360
Okay.

1189
00:42:35,070 --> 00:42:35,530
Ms. Xia.

1190
00:42:37,250 --> 00:42:38,620
Director Pan,
the one who approved the loan

1191
00:42:38,620 --> 00:42:39,150
for our Golden Sands Pool project,

1192
00:42:39,150 --> 00:42:40,400
has been called in by the head branch
for questioning.

1193
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:42,400
The bank might ask us to repay early.

1194
00:42:42,590 --> 00:42:43,120
Let's go.

1195
00:42:43,280 --> 00:42:43,920
Let's go find my uncle.

1196
00:42:43,920 --> 00:42:44,280
Okay.

1197
00:42:46,550 --> 00:42:47,480
Look, look, look!

1198
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:48,510
Look at this lobby!

1199
00:42:48,510 --> 00:42:49,370
Isn't it great?

1200
00:42:49,710 --> 00:42:51,190
After today's inspection,

1201
00:42:51,190 --> 00:42:51,920
can we

1202
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:53,380
settle the final payment?

1203
00:42:58,360 --> 00:42:59,360
This tree here...

1204
00:43:00,160 --> 00:43:02,370
This was just transplanted here.

1205
00:43:02,400 --> 00:43:03,070
The landscapers

1206
00:43:03,070 --> 00:43:04,590
haven't had time to prune it yet.

1207
00:43:04,590 --> 00:43:06,510
So the landscaping work
won't be included in the inspection?

1208
00:43:06,510 --> 00:43:06,910
No, no.

1209
00:43:07,150 --> 00:43:08,670
They'll be here to prune it soon.

1210
00:43:08,670 --> 00:43:09,230
Mr. Liu,

1211
00:43:09,440 --> 00:43:10,440
look at these details.

1212
00:43:10,440 --> 00:43:11,320
There are problems everywhere.

1213
00:43:11,320 --> 00:43:12,520
Hurry up and fix them.

1214
00:43:12,840 --> 00:43:13,640
I know, I know.

1215
00:43:13,880 --> 00:43:14,230
But...

1216
00:43:14,230 --> 00:43:15,190
Then the final payment

1217
00:43:15,190 --> 00:43:16,400
will still need to
be settled today, right?

1218
00:43:16,400 --> 00:43:16,860
Mr. Liu,

1219
00:43:17,150 --> 00:43:17,880
don't worry.

1220
00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:19,510
Once the inspection passes,

1221
00:43:19,510 --> 00:43:21,040
we will definitely pay you.

1222
00:43:21,510 --> 00:43:21,970
Wait...

1223
00:43:22,630 --> 00:43:23,430
You aren't...

1224
00:43:31,510 --> 00:43:32,040
Xiaolan!

1225
00:43:32,870 --> 00:43:34,600
-What brings you here?
-Uncle.

1226
00:43:35,440 --> 00:43:36,920
The one handling our bank loan,

1227
00:43:36,920 --> 00:43:37,550
Director Pan,

1228
00:43:37,550 --> 00:43:38,630
has been called in for questioning.

1229
00:43:38,630 --> 00:43:39,320
There wasn't anything irregular

1230
00:43:39,320 --> 00:43:40,090
in the loan process, right?

1231
00:43:40,090 --> 00:43:41,950
The process was entirely proper.

1232
00:43:43,110 --> 00:43:44,630
Is everything going smoothly here?

1233
00:43:44,630 --> 00:43:45,440
Mr. Huo

1234
00:43:45,440 --> 00:43:46,840
was supposed to do the inspection today.

1235
00:43:46,840 --> 00:43:47,590
But he said

1236
00:43:47,710 --> 00:43:49,630
something came up
and left on a business trip.

1237
00:43:49,630 --> 00:43:50,710
Isn't it obvious he's just trying to

1238
00:43:50,710 --> 00:43:52,640
avoid settling our final payment?

1239
00:43:52,710 --> 00:43:53,480
I was thinking,

1240
00:43:53,480 --> 00:43:54,230
since you're short on money now,

1241
00:43:54,230 --> 00:43:54,920
this payment would

1242
00:43:54,920 --> 00:43:56,380
at least ease things a bit.

1243
00:44:02,550 --> 00:44:03,000
Hello?

1244
00:44:07,280 --> 00:44:08,760
Okay, I got it. I'll be right there.
